title: The Ethical Omnivore Revisited (Vegan Masterpiece Theater)
description:
Shout out to Ryan Clarken, you can find his channel here:
https://www.youtube.com/user/DiscoSaladGames/videos

My own contribution to this area of discourse (i.e., heaping scorn on "Ethical Omnivores") is one of my more surreal videos, as I recall: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8a12lBXpTe0

vegan / vegans / veganism / Melanie Murphy / ecology / animal rights
